make us experimentally to know, that thou wilt eſtabliſh this thy City, thy Church for ever. So ſhall we have juſt reaſon to think of thy loving-kindneſs, and to magnifie thy mercy in the midſt of thy Temple;
Vers. 13 to praiſe thy name to the ends of the Earth, to exalt thy right-hand ſo full of righteouſneſs, to ſpeak of thy judgements, and to tell of all thy wonderous works to all generations to come.

