5. A fifth impediment, is pride of heart,

                        Ver. 5 that ſuffers not men to ſubmit their necks to the yoke of Gods Law;
Pride of heart. which impediment David doth not acknowledge in himſelf, but yet uſeth it for an Argument that he be obedient, becauſe God hates, and curſeth them, who out of pride and contempt violate his Law. Thou haſt rebuked the proud that are curſed, which do erre from thy Commandments: None with a high hand breaks them, that eſcapes unpuniſhed; not Lucifer, nor Adam.

